<p><strong>擬幻想遺物附註</strong><br />
<strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/enflowerz" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4457426); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4457426&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663833" alt="Enflowerz" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4457426)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/enflowerz" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4457426); return false;">Enflowerz</a></span></p>
